  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Controversial photo of the President of Ukraine",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The way Ukrainian President Zelensky and his wife Olana appeared in a photo in a popular American magazine has caused controversy.",
        "Russia's war on Ukraine has left thousands dead and around 10 million people have fled the country and sought refuge in neighboring countries.",
        "In this situation, President of Ukraine Zelensky and his wife Olana have given an interview to the famous American monthly magazine 'Vogue'.",
        "This interview will be published in the upcoming October issue of 'Vogue'.",
        "In the photographs published by 'Vogue' magazine, there are pictures of Olana standing in war-affected places, and pictures of Zelensky and Olana as a couple.",
        "Controversy has also arisen as to whether it is necessary to take such photographs and publish them on the Internet at the time of war. (a)"
      ],
